@startuml
[*] --> GreetUser :
GreetUser --> CheckPIN :
CheckPIN --> PINCorrect : Correct PIN entered
CheckPIN --> PINIncorrect : Incorrect PIN entered
PINCorrect --> DisplayOptions :
DisplayOptions --> WithdrawMoney : User chooses to withdraw money
DisplayOptions --> CheckInformation : User chooses to check information
DisplayOptions --> MakeTransfer : User chooses to make a transfer
WithdrawMoney --> ProcessRequest : System processes withdrawal request
CheckInformation --> ProcessRequest : System processes information request
MakeTransfer --> ProcessRequest : System processes transfer request
PINIncorrect --> TryAgain : User tries again
TryAgain --> CheckPIN :
TryAgain --> KeepCardForSecurity : Too many incorrect PIN attempts
KeepCardForSecurity --> ReturnCard : User cancels operation
ReturnCard --> GreetUser :
ProcessRequest --> [*]  // Added transition to fix missing_final_state_transition issue
@enduml
